# Alchemist Ways

## Conversion first

- Primary CTA: **Join the Waitlist** (email).
- Secondary CTA: **Book a 1-on-1 Call** — muted, not hero-equal.
- Do not add competing CTAs in the hero.

## Brand / visual

- Brand mark: **A•C** with wordmark **Alchemist Ways**. No Lovable or third-party builder logos/links.
- Paper-white / warm cream from the TanStack app styles; gold accents; no purple mystical templates.
- Signature: circular journey map (`CircularMap`). Quiet other chrome.
- See `docs/DESIGN-PRINCIPLES.md` and `docs/BRAND.md`.

## Stack

- Main app is **TanStack Start + Vite + React** at the repo root (`src/`).
- Do **not** revive the archived static `archive/legacy-landing.html` as the live site.
- Do **not** reintroduce `@lovable.dev/*`, Lovable telemetry, or `.lovable/` project metadata.

## Scope

- Landing + waitlist. No product/funnel/app scope creep unless asked.
- Prefer source/client copy over invented marketing language.
- Ask before guessing book title, booking URL, form endpoint, or brand claims.
- Read `docs/BRIEF.md`, `docs/BRAND.md`, `docs/WORKFLOW.md` before structural changes.
- Always test with `bun run dev` / `npm run dev` before push. Do not push unless the user asks.
- Update `docs/CHANGELOG.md` when shipping meaningful changes.
